# Place your images here

## Recommended images:
- profile.jpg/png - Your profile photo (500x600px recommended)
- project1.jpg/png - Project screenshot 1 (600x400px recommended)
- project2.jpg/png - Project screenshot 2 (600x400px recommended)
- project3.jpg/png - Project screenshot 3 (600x400px recommended)
- logo.svg/png - Your logo (optional)

## Usage:
Reference images in your components like:
```tsx
import Image from 'next/image'

<Image 
  src="/images/profile.jpg" 
  alt="Profile" 
  width={500}
  height={600}
/>
```
